  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then take your<strong> chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips, then add them to a baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>cumin seeds</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until crisp – these are your <strong>spiced chips</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1649173384427-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
