            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until lightly browned</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
