    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[65ml]</span> [85ml]</span> <strong>cold</strong> <strong>water</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for a further 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
