      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice </strong>in a large bowl with your <strong>harissa paste</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add your <strong>carrot & cabbage</strong> <strong>slaw mix </strong>to the bowl<strong> </strong>along with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>harissa slaw</strong></p>",
