    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked, transfer to a clean board and shred it apart, using two forks – this technique is known as ‘pulling’</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> to the pan, along with a squeeze of <strong>lemon</strong> <strong>juice,</strong> the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and<strong> mint</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>herby pulled chicken</strong></p>",
